headline: PA Health & Wellness Recognized Among Top 14 Medicaid Health Plans in the Nation by NCQA
summary: PA Health & Wellness, a leading managed care organization in Pennsylvania and a company of Centene Corporation (NYSE: CNC), today announced that it has been ranked among the top 14 Medicaid health plans in the United States by the National Committee for Quality Assurance (NCQA) in its 2025 Health Plan Ratings. This national recognition underscores the company's ongoing commitment to providing high-quality, accessible healthcare to Pennsylvanians.
